    '     MB         2. Winkel            2    75      Grad
    '     MC         3. Winkel            3    70,65   Grad
    '     MD         4. Winkel            4    55      Grad
    '     ME         5. Winkel (0/45 Grad)5    45      Grad
    '     MF         6. Winkel            6    35      Grad
    '     MG         7. Winkel            7    25      Grad
